# .gitignore
# BLUEPRINT: Composer 2 implements from this structure
# PURPOSE: Git ignore file. Excludes caches, .env, .venv, IDE artifacts, build outputs, .DS_Store.
#          Per spec §26.12 item 339. Required.
# SECTIONS:
#   - Python: __pycache__, *.pyc, *.pyo, *.pyd, .Python, build/, dist/, *.egg-info/, .eggs/
#   - Virtual environments: .venv/, venv/, env/, .env (but NOT .env.example)
#   - Testing: .pytest_cache/, .coverage, coverage.xml, htmlcov/, .tox/
#   - Type checking: .mypy_cache/, .pyright/
#   - IDE: .idea/, .vscode/, *.swp, *.swo, *~
#   - OS: .DS_Store, Thumbs.db, Desktop.ini
#   - Docker: (no build artifacts to exclude; images are external)
#   - Build: *.egg, *.egg-info, dist/, build/, .eggs/
#   - Secrets: .env (never commit real .env), *.key, *.pem, *.p12, secrets/
#   - Logs: *.log (except queue/audit.log which is tracked)
#   - Alembic: apps/api/alembic/versions/*.pyc (keep .py migration files)
# DESIGN DECISIONS:
#   - .env.example IS tracked (committed) — .env is NOT tracked
#   - queue/audit.log IS tracked (append-only evidence) — other *.log files are NOT tracked
#   - .venv is excluded; pyproject.toml defines dependencies that create it
#   - __pycache__ is always excluded including nested occurrences via **/

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
*.pyd

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
env.bak/
venv.bak/

# Environment (NEVER commit real secrets)
.env
# .env.example is committed — do not add it here

# Testing
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
.tox/
nosetests.xml
pytest-cache/

# Type checking
.mypy_cache/
.pyright/
.dmypy.json
dmypy.json

# Distribution / packaging
*.egg
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
eggs/
.eggs/
wheels/
*.spec

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.project
.classpath

# OS
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Logs (queue/audit.log is tracked; others are not)
*.log
!queue/audit.log

# Docker (local build artifacts)
.docker/

# Secrets (never commit)
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets/
secret/

# Node (for optional web/mobile profiles)
node_modules/
.npm
*.tsbuildinfo

# Temporary
tmp/
temp/
.temp/
